      "span_text": "Existing exact deterministic algorithms to compute the nodes with high betweenness centrality typically employ Dijkstra's shortest path algorithm [CITATION_1] , wherein they incorporate the dependency of a vertex on another single vertex, or the pair dependency to count the number of shortest paths"
